      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Napeague%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "The Art Barge, a retired WWII barge, now hosts the Victor D'Amico Institute of Art and operates from June through September.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
